value: Breeds: Crozet (salvini); visitor, sea: off Cape; (eremita breeds on Chatham Is)..

Breeds on Albatross Island, 30 kilometers northwest of Tas- mania, the Mewstone, south of Tasmania, and Auckland Islands (Disappointment). Migratory: ranges New Zealand and southern Australian waters and Indian Ocean, reaching South Africa. One straggler collected at lat. 47° 55' N., long. 125° 37' W., off the coast of Washington, United States.
